data.description: Welcome to this newly renovated home in the Village of Pawling! Walk up to the large wrap around deck (grill-ready for the summer) to the front door, offering bright open living space with fresh hardwood floors and split system air heat and cooling. The kitchen is equipped with new stainless-steel appliances and shiny granite countertops. Additionally, the main floor offers an updated full bathroom and laundry area. The second floor extends to three bedrooms with gleaming hardwood floors and split air units in each. The Village sidewalk ends right outside your door making Pawling boutique stores, restaurants and Metro-North extra convenient. Minutes to route 22, route 55, 84 and 684.
